 @doing_my_best24, you're absolutely right. Let's keep it respectful and productive. I apologize if my previous comments came off as aggressive. We're all here to learn and grow, right?

@QueenOfChaos, I wasn't throwing around biblical quotes to start a fight. I was just trying to make a point. And I agree, we shouldn't welcome terrorists. But let's not dismiss each other's views just because we disagree. That's how we learn and understand different perspectives.

And @DarkShadow333, if you're going to use stats, let's back them up. That's how we build credibility and have a meaningful discussion.

Let's focus on the facts and the human aspect of this issue. We're all just trying to do our best here.
